rman installation
=================

Prerequisites
-------------

* Ruby version 1.9.3 or later

Installation
------------

1. Download and extract the latest release:

        curl -O https://github.com/thoughtbot/rman/releases/download/v@PACKAGE_VERSION@/rman-@PACKAGE_VERSION@.tar.gz
        tar -zxvf rman-@PACKAGE_VERSION@.tar.gz
        cd rman-@PACKAGE_VERSION@

2. Configure the distribution.

        ./configure

3. Build and install rman:

        make
        sudo make install
